source.name: Public Budget Database - Governmental receipts 1962-Current
source.description: This file contains governmental receipts for 1962 through the current budget year, as well as four years of projections. It can be used to reproduce many of the totals published in the Budget and examine unpublished details below the levels of aggregation published in the Budget.
